有耶穌<br />\n又有艾法同愛華頓<br />\n起碼兩至三年都無太大影響<br />\n睇下有冇人在右翼接到艾維斯"},{"pid":"beafaefdab5bb9cf73c7de16d97e42314be89707","tid":1280561,"uid":61372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:56:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬係鍠黎 好賤 扮阿反疤<br />\n同黑警扮示威者一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996bf3658a64175312dcdebe26c697ba07fb034a","tid":1280561,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:46:27.000Z","msg":"11歐國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}